{"tid":1706902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"十 一 月 十 二 日 繼 續 大 三 罷","createTime":"2019-11-11T07:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T15:17:34.000Z","uid":46984,"like":94,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"3e1241eb5a982c551ea1d51ef3c1c3079b17b121","tid":1706902,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"聽日好似未有定案 今日就好成功<br />\n全香港全部黃絲罷工都應該夠做<br />\n<br />\n希望黃絲上司/老闆放風支持或者幫幫手帶頭罷工 有第一間就有第二間架啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">冇人/唔夠時間罷又有小朋友出黎抗爭受傷</span></span><br />\n每個人做少少佢地起碼唔洗又跪又盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋見有POST推八大永久罷課<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">D狗沖入大學都係唔想大家返學咁不如大家都唔好返啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外今日有太多事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足中槍同警犬亂撞人既post都開始沉</span></span><br />\n麻煩各位係FB 同IG 最起碼都推一推返上黎<br />\n火魔法要留意 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過警犬變本加厲都唔可以由佢沉</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">之前開post都係自己推唔上 岩聽就推多幾次<br />\n唔岩聽就由佢沉<br />\n岩岩打錯左日期開過</span>"},{"pid":"5fa746b0354239579d26efd5b7610173d276746c","tid":1706902,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"冇人推我自己推"},{"pid":"8631089a728ceb5fc29385f2d5fbe7cf3e1d8544","tid":1706902,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4344e6286a487f688ac9406aad3f3a1f67fb736","tid":1706902,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"[12/11 黎明行動] 聽朝06:00am 繼續塞路三罷<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1706691\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1706691</a>"},{"pid":"e000ede5fd06c3577f8779ff86c126f1e1ce020d","tid":1706902,"uid":1